headline: Rocket acquires Mr. Cooper, Musk’s xAI acquires X: Morning Buzz
summary: The major averages were mostly lower near noon, with the Dow up fractionally but the Nasdaq down nearly 250 points amid mounting concerns about President Donald Trump’s upcoming announcement of promised new tariffs. Meanwhile, the S&P 500’s early losses brought the index to its lowest level since September.
